I am trying the below code on iverilog 10.2. build and see error as below. Am I missing a switch or is this support not yet there in Icarus?

Thanks
Srini

--- Error --
iverilog ../ref/inherit_base.sv -g2012 
../ref/inherit_base.sv:51: assert: elab_scope.cc:512: failed assertion scope
sh: line 1: 22155 Done                    /usr/lib64/ivl/ivlpp -L -F"/tmp/ivrlg2550493e9" -f"/tmp/ivrlg550493e9" -p"/tmp/ivrli550493e9"
     22156 Aborted                 (core dumped) | /usr/lib64/ivl/ivl -C"/tmp/ivrlh550493e9" -C"/usr/lib64/ivl/vvp.conf" -

---- Code:              
 
class s2p_pkt;
 bit [15:0] hdr= 16'd10;
 bit [15:0] pkt_pld=16'd30;

  virtual function bit [31:0] bit_pack();
      bit_pack = {hdr,pkt_pld};
  endfunction : bit_pack

  function void display ();
    $display ("CVC:VSV: Lab3: Learning Inheritence");
    $display ("CVC:VSV: Lab3: Extended class %m has base properties hdr %0b pkt_pld %0b AND Extra err_pkt ", hdr, pkt_pld );
  endfunction : display

endclass : s2p_pkt

class s2p_err_pkt extends s2p_pkt;
endclass

